      • getMaxSupportedTotalSlots

        public int getMaxSupportedTotalSlots()

        the maximum number of slots

      • getVariableSupported

        public int getVariableSupported()
        Get the field encoding the following properties:
        - IS_VARIABLE_ADV_SUPPORTED. Set if the beacon supports individual per-slot advertising intervals. Not set if the beacon supports only a global advertising interval.
        - IS_VARIABLE_TX_POWER_SUPPORTED. Set if the beacon supports individual per-slot Tx powers. Not set if the beacon supports only a single global Tx power.
        Returns:
        the value encoding variable values.
